{"id":"5360d18a-af41-4bb2-903b-3066d0474041","name":"Deidara | Akatsuki","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 156, 156)\">〃Tᴇʀʀᴏʀɪsᴛ!Bᴏᴛ x Pʟᴏᴛ Oʀɪᴇɴᴛᴇᴅ!Usᴇʀ<br>〃Tᴇᴍᴘᴏʀᴀʀʏ Bᴀʙʏsɪᴛᴛᴇʀ<br>〃Aᴋᴀᴛsᴜᴋɪ Sᴇʀɪᴇs<br>〃AɴʏPOV </span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 75, 75)\">┍———————-</span> 💣 <span style=\"color: rgb(75, 75, 75)\">———————┑</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/bdbe8839-927c-48dc-8af9-08a3eb475597_3f3b096a-20fb-48e8-838d-42ceb49ba90c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>After the brutal lesson from Pain</em></strong>, your doubts about Akatsuki’s philosophy have been silenced, and there’s no time for reflection. Itachi, your current duo, is on another mission, and you’ve been immediately assigned to your next task alongside Deidara, the unpredictable and chaotic <em>Mad Bomber</em>. This is clearly a test of your <em>loyalty</em> to Pain: if you hesitated to eliminate your targets before, now it’s <em>impossible</em> to try and protect them. Either you accept the thorns on the path to <strong><em>true peace</em></strong>, or... Well, <em>you know</em>.</span><br><br>🔗 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\">Akatsuki Series</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(156, 156, 156)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\">【</mark></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\">Initial Route</mark></em><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #00000000; color: inherit\">】</mark></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8f00ca71-d8a8-46ad-94e5-ed7868e6e128_character-itachi-uchiha-akatsuki\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Itachi</strong></a><span style=\"color: